org.sql: SELECT users.* FROM users WHERE users.type IN ('User', 'AnonymousUser') AND users.status = "$1" AND (users.id = 6 OR users.id IN (SELECT user_id FROM members WHERE project_id IN (1, 3, 4, 6))) AND users.status = "$2" AND users.id = "$3" LIMIT "$4"
